  "texts": [
    "As can be noticed, decreasing the value of the thresholds reduces the isolated nodes and increases the number of edges.",
    "In this way, it is possible to connect more patients due to the possibility of creating an edge between two nodes with some more dissimilarities.",
    "We first generated patient networks using Euclidean Distance to define edges.",
    "We used different thresholds (0.20, 0.23, 0.25,0.28,0.31, 0.38).",
    "In this case, an edge connects two nodes when the Euclidean distance is lower than the threshold."
